Cybil moved over to the man until she was able to look down at him, and then folded her arms.[p]
She was relieved.[p]
That was how she honestly felt.[p]
"It looks like you have come around."[p]
"Who are you?"[p]
The man asked this while heavily shaking his head.[p]
"I'm Cybil.[p]
Cybil Bennet.[p]
All communication with this town suddenly went dead. [p]
This worried me, so I came here to investigate."[p]
"I'm...Harry Mason. [p]
I brought my daughter to this town for some sightseeing, but on the way, there was an accident and I lost consciousness...[p]
Oh, yeah, Cybil...You haven't seen a little girl in this town have you?"[p]


