"So you also had an accident?[p]
I thought it was a good idea to head to the police station in this town alone on my motorcycle, but...[p]
I guess I was going a little too fast.[p]
A girl suddenly jumped out into the road...I am pretty sure it was a girl...I almost hit her.[p]
I cut the handlebars hard in order to avoid her...[p]
After that, I can barely remember anything......[p]
When I came to, I was lying in the street in front of this cafe.[p]
So naturally, I came in here to get out of the snow.[p]
And then I found you sleeping there..."[p]
"I...was having some kind of a terrible dream.[p]
As for if I made it here on my own, I don't remember at all...[p]
Just what in the world has happened in this town...[p]
What is going on with everything?"[p]
"Well, the situation is definitely strange.[p]
I will head back to Brahms for reinforcements, and then return here.[p]
How about you?"[p]
Cybil stood and fixed her collar with resolute fortitude.[p]


